,"tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"練返啲基本scale先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"多謝大佬回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬我應該點入手好? 跪求講深入講解...<br />\n例如搵咩譜、點練之類..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"借問一聲你好想拉嘅嘢例如係咩？古典音樂？流行曲？"},{"pid":"15fd1f1140b9989f286b217d4aa21e32cf56ad19","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4311fb6af600af7649ab172c4acdd76adf5eb639","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7824966814f465956b54fe32e46302a307b9b417","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e36b2976cc5c39362b23cb9c0352cfd5483658f","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"練返啲基本scale先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"多謝大佬回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬我應該點入手好? 跪求講深入講解...<br />\n例如搵咩譜、點練之類..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"借問一聲你好想拉嘅嘢例如係咩？古典音樂？流行曲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意電影配樂同一D小品。<br />\n<br />\n例如: Cinema Paradiso love theme(電影配樂), Liebeslied (小提琴小品)<br />\n<br />\n當然,大作品好似Mendelssohn concerto 呢 D梗想...不過廢到連恨都好似有罪咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb64b4a737d284c63adae6fc5cd3657501edf3","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15fd1f1140b9989f286b217d4aa21e32cf56ad19","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4311fb6af600af7649ab172c4acdd76adf5eb639","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7824966814f465956b54fe32e46302a307b9b417","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"多謝大佬回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬我應該點入手好? 跪求講深入講解...<br />\n例如搵咩譜、點練之類..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"借問一聲你好想拉嘅嘢例如係咩？古典音樂？流行曲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意電影配樂同一D小品。<br />\n<br />\n例如: Cinema Paradiso love theme(電影配樂), Liebeslied (小提琴小品)<br />\n<br />\n當然,大作品好似Mendelssohn concerto 呢 D梗想...不過廢到連恨都好似有罪咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"嘩 師兄你都幾大野心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCinema Paradiso love theme有好多換把位可能連八級甚至ATCL都未必應付得到<br />\n<br />\nLiebeslied可能好少少，但拉得好聽亦唔容易，因為慢歌需要好細緻嘅音色控制，而控制得最基本就係音準<br />\n<br />\n如果想練好音準，首先要練聽力<br />\n我自己有一個方法以前用過，就係搵一首唔係太難又喜歡嘅歌（例如流行曲），然後響唔睇譜嘅情況下搵音，淨係用耳仔學。咁樣可以潛移默化地迫自己去搵正確嘅音<br />\n<br />\n不過即使係被上天揀選嘅音樂天才，或者有perfect pitch，萬變不離其宗都係需要有老師帶著成長；因此<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最折衷嘅方法都係搵個老師</span></span>幫你練好基本功，因為學音樂從來都冇捷徑"},{"pid":"cb927a0d721064630b583b757320d8999807ba20","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cb64b4a737d284c63adae6fc5cd3657501edf3","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15fd1f1140b9989f286b217d4aa21e32cf56ad19","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4311fb6af600af7649ab172c4acdd76adf5eb639","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"借問一聲你好想拉嘅嘢例如係咩？古典音樂？流行曲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意電影配樂同一D小品。<br />\n<br />\n例如: Cinema Paradiso love theme(電影配樂), Liebeslied (小提琴小品)<br />\n<br />\n當然,大作品好似Mendelssohn concerto 呢 D梗想...不過廢到連恨都好似有罪咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"嘩 師兄你都幾大野心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCinema Paradiso love theme有好多換把位可能連八級甚至ATCL都未必應付得到<br />\n<br />\nLiebeslied可能好少少，但拉得好聽亦唔容易，因為慢歌需要好細緻嘅音色控制，而控制得最基本就係音準<br />\n<br />\n如果想練好音準，首先要練聽力<br />\n我自己有一個方法以前用過，就係搵一首唔係太難又喜歡嘅歌（例如流行曲），然後響唔睇譜嘅情況下搵音，淨係用耳仔學。咁樣可以潛移默化地迫自己去搵正確嘅音<br />\n<br />\n不過即使係被上天揀選嘅音樂天才，或者有perfect pitch，萬變不離其宗都係需要有老師帶著成長；因此<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最折衷嘅方法都係搵個老師</span></span>幫你練好基本功，因為學音樂從來都冇捷徑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:37:29.000Z","msg":"宮崎駿嘅音樂係唔錯嘅選擇"},{"pid":"f3dda8088b51abc051af9cb2ba74b04cdf1bceb5","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73cb64b4a737d284c63adae6fc5cd3657501edf3","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15fd1f1140b9989f286b217d4aa21e32cf56ad19","tid":1375623,"uid":279870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4311fb6af600af7649ab172c4acdd76adf5eb639","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:12.000Z","msg":"借問一聲你好想拉嘅嘢例如係咩？古典音樂？流行曲？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意電影配樂同一D小品。<br />\n<br />\n例如: Cinema Paradiso love theme(電影配樂), Liebeslied (小提琴小品)<br />\n<br />\n當然,大作品好似Mendelssohn concerto 呢 D梗想...不過廢到連恨都好似有罪咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"嘩 師兄你都幾大野心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCinema Paradiso love theme有好多換把位可能連八級甚至ATCL都未必應付得到<br />\n<br />\nLiebeslied可能好少少，但拉得好聽亦唔容易，因為慢歌需要好細緻嘅音色控制，而控制得最基本就係音準<br />\n<br />\n如果想練好音準，首先要練聽力<br />\n我自己有一個方法以前用過，就係搵一首唔係太難又喜歡嘅歌（例如流行曲），然後響唔睇譜嘅情況下搵音，淨係用耳仔學。咁樣可以潛移默化地迫自己去搵正確嘅音<br />\n<br />\n不過即使係被上天揀選嘅音樂天才，或者有perfect pitch，萬變不離其宗都係需要有老師帶著成長；因此<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最折衷嘅方法都係搵個老師</span></span>幫你練好基本功，因為學音樂從來都冇捷徑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"哈 唔洗客氣,直接D屌我大撚頭都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我都知係大撚頭左D...<br />\n<br />\n其實我都明白自己學同練好易錯同有局限,所以都有搵老師學既。<br />\n<br />\n不過因為番工要輪班,練同上堂都勁疏(2個星期到甚至半年一次有試過),我個老師都知,所以每次都俾勁多野練。而且自己蠢<del>加少少覺得老師表達能力有問題</del>,進度慢到已經唔係單純可以非常慢黎形容。廢既程度去到心思思想拉6級既考試歌(Ladies in Lavender)都拉唔到,而只係有能力拉番以前五級既考試歌同程度差唔多既野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9eccd7fa641fb3aa66d9cdc7e5c73f10bf7158","tid":1375623,"uid":247046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3dda8088b51abc051af