gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:14:42.000Z","msg":"如果師兄你知道嘅咁我都無謂屌你啦，我明白生活艱難嘅。總之就係即使幾忙都好，都盡量抽時間出嚟練琴啦，加油！"},{"pid":"1f45b8cde36d3d3efa206cf3e732056a39f858b7","tid":1375623,"uid":270761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:44:49.000Z","msg":"每次練之前都用5分鐘左右拉下空弦，拉scale果陣又可以練分弓同連弓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}